(f)  provisions  for  the  ventilation  of  buildings  for  the 
purpose  of  removing  gases  and  smoke  that  may  be 
caused by a fire;

(g)  provisions  for  fire  fighting  equipment  both  manual 
and automatic and of fire detectors and fire alarms and 
